  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"big-one-two\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">獵豹 朱安強博士</span><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:28px;\"><br />\n帶給孩子們一堂精彩的Python體驗課</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:22px;\">大家一起來上課!</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\"></span></strong></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BwMGi1V4Rng?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>朱老師Python課程的特色是，大量舉數學上的例子，結合Python的應用，剛好非常適合喜歡數理的孩子們，做為接觸程式語言的入門學習方式。<br />\n<br />\n例如昨天公開課上，從一開始老師讓孩子們知道Python是個威力強大的計算機， 可以做各種運算。老師還舉了拉馬努金的故事，讓孩子學習的不只有程式，還有Python X Math的結合，更能感染老師深厚的人文素養氣質。朱老師在獵豹Python課堂中，常舉各升學考題如科學班考題為例，解說如何做驗證，以及如何利用Python來做數學探究，也介紹Turtle利用迴圈來創作數學藝術，相信昨天參與的孩子們都很有收穫，也對Python和數學有更深一層的認識！<br />\n<br />\n謝謝老師為我們帶來這麼棒的體驗課程，也和獵豹網課一樣提供課後回放，讓孩子學習和複習。<br />\n​​​​​​​<br />\n星媽社團的資源，都歡迎大家多分享，也為自己的孩子找到相同興趣的學伴喔！</span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></span></span><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\"></editor-squiggler></p>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n</editor-squiggler></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></p>\n<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/963643807921638/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/963643807921638/</a>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n</div>",
